Instructions for Using pdb:

Run the script: When you run the script, it will pause execution at pdb.set_trace().

Step through the code:
Use n to execute the next line.
Use c to continue execution until the next breakpoint.

Inspect variables:
Type student_records to view the processed list after the calculate_totals_and_averages function.
Type scholarship_candidates to check the list of qualifying students.

Debug specific lines:
Use l to view the source code around the current breakpoint.
Set additional breakpoints with break <line_number>.